profileAlternative.headline: Helping companies realize their strategic initiatives in order to create a competitive advantage.
profileAlternative.summary: I'm an energetic, goal-oriented individual who thrives under pressure. I lead by example and have consistently advanced my career through a relentless work ethic, evidenced by multiple promotions at both Enterprise and MongoDB. Outside of work, I'm a native Texan driven by music, travel, family, friends, and Dad jokes. I gravitate towards competition and sports (playing and watching) are largely how I spend my free time.
